                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-19-off120 t18190217-19-cd121"></join>, one pair of boots, value 14 s.; one great coat value, 2 l. 10 s., and one hat, value 1 l., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190217-19-victim242" type="victimName">
